# UIUserInterfaceLevel.unspecified

**Case**

An unspecified interface level.

## Declaration

```swift
case unspecified
```

## Discussion

Choose this option when you want to follow the inherited level.

## Interface levels

- **UIUserInterfaceLevel.base**: The level for your window’s main content.
- **UIUserInterfaceLevel.elevated**: The level for content visually above your window’s main content.
